r-shy-3464950">《Super Shy》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-transform-into-the-powerpuff-girls-in-new-jeans-mv-3465954">《New Jeans》</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jung-ho-yeon-tony-leung-newjeans-cool-with-you-music-video-3470889">由郑浩妍、梁朝伟主演的 NewJeans 音乐录影带《Cool With You》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
